@startuml jinnerbichler_flash-home

actor User
participant "Home Assistant" as HA
participant "Coffee Machine Client" as CMC
participant "Coffee Machine Flash Server" as CMFS
participant "Provider Flash Server" as PFS
participant "IOTA Testnet" as IOTA
database MongoDB

User -> HA : Trigger coffee brewing
activate HA
HA -> CMC : Send MQTT message
activate CMC

CMC -> CMFS : Initialize/update flash channel
activate CMFS
CMFS <-> PFS : Negotiate channel state
activate PFS
CMFS -> MongoDB : Store channel state
PFS -> MongoDB : Store channel state
CMFS --> CMC : Channel ready
deactivate CMFS
deactivate PFS

CMC -> CMC : Brew coffee

CMC -> CMFS : Sign transaction
activate CMFS
CMFS <-> PFS : Exchange signatures
CMFS -> MongoDB : Update channel state
PFS -> MongoDB : Update channel state
CMFS --> CMC : Transaction complete
deactivate CMFS

CMC --> HA : Update coffee status
deactivate CMC

HA -> User : Display updated status
deactivate HA

note right of IOTA
  Flash channels settle
  on the IOTA network
  periodically or on closure
end note

@enduml